5 Light'; font-size:11pt">recent </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">NHS reforms</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> it is crucial that attention is given to the provision of accurate, reputable advice on how to manage a LTC. This information can be used to empower a patient (or their carer) to take responsibility for their own condition and optimise their personal management.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">7</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">It is critical that patients have access to cost-effective innovation as part of an integrated pathway of care and that CCGs are measured, incentivised and rewarded for delivering excellence in the care of patients with LTCs. Uptake of new technologies that improve outcomes must be central to this in the new NHS.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Diabetes</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal">8</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The scale of the challenge that diabetes presents in the UK should not be underestim